description: All too soon Mikey's vacation is over, but he's not sad because he realizes that he's fallen in love with his best friend Sabastian, and that Sabastian cares for him too. On their last night in paradise, they share passionate love making that seals their new bond and brings our story to a close!
title: CitiBoyz 37: Skaterboyz Diaries 2, Scene #07
